      "bron": "HAVO Engels CE 2023 Tijdvak 1 Woordenschat & Grammatica (geen afbeelding)",
      "ctx": "Fill-in context:\n\n\"If the government __ (introduce) stricter pollution laws ten years ago, the air quality __ (be) much better today. Many scientists agree that the delay __ (cost) the environment dearly.\"",
